The paper deals with bias in machine learning, which is a common topic in the subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses fairness in classification, which is relevant to the subfield of cybersecurity (cs.CY). The paper proposes a mathematical formulation to correct label bias, which is related to the subfield of cryptography (cs.CR). Finally, the paper evaluates its method on fairness datasets, which is relevant to computer vision (cs.CV).
